{"tid":2354338,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本考慮全面禁止外國人入境　包含商務人士","createTime":"2021-01-05T11:53:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T12:08:08.000Z","uid":75656,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"96436f032c3372f65999152d5f260f370592ebed","tid":2354338,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T11:53:51.000Z","msg":"日本政府為防止2019冠狀病毒疾病（COVID-19，武漢肺炎）疫情擴大，12月26日宣布對全球暫停放寬邊境管制，但仍與包括台灣、中國、韓國等11國保持商務相關人士等的往來。不過，如果外國發現新變種病毒株市區感染，就暫停這個國家的外籍人士新申請入境。<br />\n<br />\n「朝日新聞」報導，首相菅義偉昨天上午在記者會上說，如果對方國發現新變種病毒株，立即暫停該國外籍人士新申請入境。但這項發言遭到日本朝野政黨批評，政府因此改變方針，不管對方國是否發現新變種病毒株，考慮全面禁止外籍人士申請入境。<br />\n<br />\n日本政府正研議全面禁止外籍人士申請入境的期間，至少是在「緊急事態宣言」實施期將全面暫停外籍人士新申請入境。<br />\n<br />\n日本政府快則本月7日發布緊急事態宣言。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210105/L3N6MUCV3FDPHLOFHRSE7DRZYU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210105%2FL3N6MUCV3FDPHLOFHRSE7DRZYU%2F&d=QL2FFPepynYtbGyOTzoAG0wAUq3ZsepC89uAf1Ef2WI%3D&h=7cdc43cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210105%2FL3N6MUCV3FDPHLOFHRSE7DRZYU%2F&h=85ffe3a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210105/L3N6MUCV3FDPHLOFHRSE7DRZYU/</a>"},{"pid":"f1c31e149e3816a834f5e01d7b1af6c5e73f9e6b","tid":2354338,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T11:55:27.000Z","msg":"佢地自己國內都夠哂爆啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb53329cdfe6351a52db373ae3a8e3b36097ed3e","tid":2354338,"uid":66087,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T11:56:55.000Z","msg":"<strong>但仍與包括台灣、中國、韓國等11國保持商務相關人士等的往來。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf7f98d086740c1eb14631f6a6ddf5f0f8594fdc","t